Cargo.lock

# napi-rs build output
#
# The binary itself is not committed — it is platform-specific and weighs megabytes.
# index.js (the loader that picks the right platform package) and index.d.ts (the
# native layer's types) ARE committed: they are generated deterministically from the
# Rust sources, consumers of the package need them, and CI jobs that do not build the
# addon require them (typecheck, tests against a downloaded artifact, docker images).
# Their freshness is verified in CI by diffing after a build.
*.node

# Node
node_modules
npm-debug.log*

# TypeScript build output
/dist


# Platform package directories (generated by napi create-npm-dirs)
/npm
